  <td class="diff-context"><div>[[File:Brennus mg 9724.jpg|thumb|The Gallic leader [[Brennus (4th century)|Brennus]], as depicted on the [[figurehead (object)|figurehead]] of the [[French battleship Brennus|battleship named after him]]]]</div></td>
